{
  "texts": [
    "During the trial, each side presents their opening statements, introduces evidence (through witnesses and exhibits), and presents a closing statement.",
    "Unless otherwise decided, the civil jury will contain at least six members and their decision must be unanimous (Weinberger et al. 2023). foot_12",
    "A securities class action case begins when a plaintiff files a securities class action complaint.",
    "If similar actions have already been brought, the plaintiffs may decide to consolidate them.",
    "The court appoints a \"lead plaintiff\" for the class action."
  ]
}